- This repository exists to build GroundSealOperatorConsole, not a general-purpose agent platform.
- Keep work aligned to the subsystem focus: approval review UX, run timelines, trace visibility, evidence browsing, redaction-aware presentation, and tenant-safe operator flows.
- Before implementation, map each task to a roadmap phase.
- Do not add neighboring subsystems unless the integration contract explicitly requires it.
- Favor clarity, contracts, and evaluability over scope growth.
